750
00:53:12,682 --> 00:53:14,517
Come on, Mom.

751
00:53:15,059 --> 00:53:17,228
I still have so much, but you sent more?

752
00:53:37,665 --> 00:53:40,043
How can a bracelet cost 10 million won?

753
00:53:41,920 --> 00:53:45,048
Why didn't she demand compensation?
Is it because she's rich?

754
00:53:52,096 --> 00:53:53,181
Who is this?

755
00:53:54,057 --> 00:53:56,768
-You're here early.
-Mr. Jeong called.

756
00:53:56,851 --> 00:53:58,811
-I heard you called--
